{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/84/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/84.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/84/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/84/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/issues/84/branch-drcsim_10-is-broken-with-gazebo-131"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/84/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/109284c8b83411dbc7492138f6167e9ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJR-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Jose Luis Rivero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:155a32e2-420c-4d50-98e0-0e722f63f906"}, "title": "Branch drcsim_1.0 is broken with gazebo-1.3.1 and default", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 1, "content": {"raw": "Branch 1.0 is currently broken with gazebo-1.3.1.  Probably, at any time, gazebo change the name of a header from physics.h to physics.hh. Branch drcsim_1.0 is using the .h and it does not exists anymore.\r\n\r\nFix is easy with a one liner in the top directory:\r\n\r\n```\r\n#!bash\r\n\r\nfind \\( -name \"*.h\" -o -name \"*.hh\" \\) -exec sed -i -e 's:physics.h\":physics.hh\":g' {} \\;\r\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Branch 1.0 is currently broken with gazebo-1.3.1.  Probably, at any time, gazebo change the name of a header from physics.h to physics.hh. Branch drcsim_1.0 is using the .h and it does not exists anymore.</p>\n<p>Fix is easy with a one liner in the top directory:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-bash\"><pre><span></span>find <span class=\"se\">\\(</span> -name <span class=\"s2\">&quot;*.h&quot;</span> -o -name <span class=\"s2\">&quot;*.hh&quot;</span> <span class=\"se\">\\)</span> -exec sed -i -e <span class=\"s1\">&#39;s:physics.h&quot;:physics.hh&quot;:g&#39;</span> <span class=\"o\">{}</span> <span class=\"se\">\\;</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-01-10T12:06:10.189909+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-01-12T02:02:36.145214+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 84}